{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"💝"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"但你身邊的人可能需要幫助"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"你的朋友、同事、家人，可能正在經歷上面某一種代謝困擾。他們可能覺得是自己意志力不夠、不夠努力、或是身體壞掉了。\n\n你可以把這份測驗傳給他們。也許你已經知道的事，正好是他們需要聽到的——「不是你的錯，是方法不對。」"}]]}]]}]}],null,["$","section",null,{"className":"py-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-6","children":["💡 給","穩定燃燒","的你"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","div","0",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#27ae60"},"children":1}],"你現在的狀態不錯，但代謝是動態的。繼續保持就是最好的策略。"]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#27ae60"},"children":2}],"你可能覺得自己沒什麼特別的——但能夠好好吃飯、好好睡覺、好好過生活，在現在這個時代就是一種了不起的能力。"]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#27ae60"},"children":3}],"把這個測驗傳給你身邊那個正在跟體重苦戰的朋友。也許他需要的不是更多意志力，而是知道「不是他的錯」。"]}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 px-5 bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-xl mx-auto text-center","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[#6b6560] mb-2","children":"你不用一個人搞懂這些"}